<title>GREECE: Athens bourse okays Kekrops rights issue.</title>
<headline>Athens bourse okays Kekrops rights issue.</headline>
<dateline>ATHENS 1997-02-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Athens stock exchange said on Thursday it had approved a 419 million drachma rights issue by cement maker Kekrops.</p>
<p>Kekrops will issue 167,688 new ordinary registered shares at 2,500 drachmas. Rights will entitle shareholders to 17 new shares for every 100 outstanding.</p>
<p>Proceeds will finance the company's construction activities. --George Georgiopoulos, Athens Newsroom +301 3311812-4</p>
